data.title: Federal Reserve Board
meta_keywords: Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System
data.meta_description: The Federal Reserve Board of Governors in Washington DC.
data.text: The Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System and the Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis's Federal Reserve Economic Data (FRED) program are working together to expand options for finding, accessing, and visualizing data from the Board's Data Download Program (DDP) in FRED. Learn more about the DDP and FRED partnership .
